# Optional local overrides for Booking.com MCP wrappers.
#
# NPX=npx
# MCPORTER=mcporter
# BOOKING_TIMEOUT=180000
#
# Browser/session defaults used by @striderlabs/mcp-booking:
# - Node.js 18+ is required.
# - Playwright Chromium may be installed with: npx playwright install chromium
# - Login cookies, if you ever use login manually, are stored under ~/.strider/booking/.
